<p class="p76"><span class="c0">Serve and measure the effectiveness of advertising;</span></p>
<p class="p77"><span class="c0">Measure the health of our services;</span></p>
<p class="p78"><span class="c0">Set up and maintain accounts you register for;</span></p>
<p class="p79"><span class="c0">Provide game experiences that you may like;</span></p>
