<p class="p81"><span class="c0">Facilitate your gameplay on multiple devices when available;</span></p>
<p class="p82"><span class="c0">Identify, fix, and troubleshoot bugs and service errors;</span></p>
<p class="p83"><span class="c0">Provide software updates;</span></p>
<p class="p84"><span class="c0">Activate or authenticate your games and save game progress and stats;</span></p>
<p class="p85"><span class="c0">Adhere to your preferences and to deliver dynamic content</span></p>
<p class="p86"><span class="c0">Help keep our games safe and fair and comply with the law.</span></p>
